ally generated in spring boot, by back-end in asp.net core. For the front-end all the common language can be used (angular, react), including Blazor.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-17T10:04:10.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Podcasts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://expect-exception.fail/podcast/3\">Blazor in Action with Chris Sainty</a> - November 17, 2020 - In this episode of expect(Exception) we talk with Chris Sainty, author of the book Blazor in Action. We talk about what Blazor actually is, why we like it and of course, how to test it. <a href=\"https://www.manning.com/books/blazor-in-action\">Blazor in Action</a>'s book.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-17T09:58:57.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"fkromer/awesome-ros2","categoryHTML":"<h2>Packages</h2><h3>Driver layer</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://docs.blickfeld.com/cube/latest/external/ros/driver-v2/README.html\">Blickfeld Cube 1 &#x26; Cube Range</a> - ROS2 drivers for Blickfeld Cube 1 &#x26; Cube Range.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-17T09:45:08.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"vuejs/awesome-vue","categoryHTML":"<h2>Components &#x26; Libraries</h2><h4>Calendar</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jinfang134/vue-schedule-board\">vue-schedule-board</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jinfang134/vue-schedule-board\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":12,\"repo\":\"jinfang134/vue-schedule-board\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_